{"ID":"20260305082130-ft8km65","Spec":"2","Type":"NodeDocument","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ft8km65","title":"类与对象","type":"doc","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082201-04ty6mi","Type":"NodeCodeBlock","Properties":{"id":"20260305082201-04ty6mi"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceOpenMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceInfoMarker","CodeBlockInfo":"eWFtbA=="},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockCode","Data":"---\ntitle: 类与对象\ndate created: 星期一, 十月 20日 2025, 9:52:15 上午\ndate modified: 星期四, 十月 23日 2025, 9:06:11 晚上\n---"},{"Type":"NodeCodeBlockFenceCloseMarker","Data":"```","CodeBlockFenceLen":3}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ynugxb0","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ynugxb0","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类与对象"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-r1or0d3","Type":"NodeParagraph","Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-r1or0d3","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"C++ 是面向对象的程序设计语言，具有 封装、继承、多态的特性，而其关键就是类。"},{"Type":"NodeSoftBreak","Data":"\n"},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"类是创建对象的蓝图或模板。它定义了对象的属性（数据成员）和行为（成员函数）。通过类，我们可以将数据和操作数据的方法封装在一起，形成一个独立的单元。这有助于实现代码的模块化、重用性和可维护性。"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-ebya0qi","Type":"NodeHeading","HeadingLevel":1,"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-ebya0qi","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"Type":"NodeHeadingC8hMarker","Data":"# "},{"Type":"NodeText","Data":"更多内容"}]},{"ID":"20260305082130-0r9mqfy","Type":"NodeList","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-0r9mqfy","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-tjzjcjx","Type":"NodeListItem","Data":"1.","ListData":{"Typ":1,"Tight":true,"Start":1,"Delimiter":46,"Padding":3,"Marker":"MS4=","Num":1},"Properties":{"id":"20260305082130-tjzjcjx","updated":"20260305082130"},"Children":[{"ID":"20260305082130-bhpqyv0","Ty